## 💡 The Bottom Line

> **Don't try to out-feature OpenClaw** (they have 247K stars and OpenAI backing).  
> **Don't try to out-optimize PicoClaw** (you share the same Go codebase).  
> 
> Instead, **own a market they ignore** (South Asia), **ship features they haven't** (voice, offline, visual), and **win on experience** (beautiful UI, easy setup, Urdu-first).
>
> The Gryphon doesn't chase — it strikes from above. 🦅
